7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Codium AI and Phind share a solid foundation of core features including Debugging, Multi Language, Ide Integration. Where Codium AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Code Review and Test Generation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Phind uniquely offers Code Generation and Chat, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Codium AI holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Phind scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Phind comes in at a lower starting price of $17/mo, while Codium AI begins at $19/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Codium AI's free tier and Phind's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
